2014;;Apocalypse Pompeii;;American;;Ben Demaree;;Adrian PaulJohn Rhys-DaviesDylan Vox;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apocalypse_Pompeii;;When a Former Special Ops commando visits Pompeii, Italy, his wife and daughter are trapped as Mount Vesuvius erupts with massive force. While his family fights to survive the deadly onslaught of heat and lava, he enlists his former teammates in a daring operation beneath the ruins of Pompeii.